=== Installing Ruby 1.8 ===

Follow the instructions on http://www.ruby-lang.org/en/downloads/, in particular, if you use Ubuntu Linux then use:

% sudo apt-get install ruby irb rdoc

=== Installing Ruby-GNOME 2 ===
Follow the instructions on http://ruby-gnome2.sourceforge.jp/hiki.cgi?Install+Guide, in particular, if you use Ubuntu Linus then use:

% sudo apt-get install ruby-gnome2

=== Using the program ===
In the command line, run:

% ruby robotplanning.rb

